Some advantages of TAP for the region include:
 Independent, non-discriminatory and open for third parties and private investments,;
 Deepening the diversification and security of gas supply in Europe,;
 Potential for enlargement of new and additional projects,;
 Built-in concept of flexibility by construction of gas storage in Albania.;

Some advantages of IAP for the region include:
 Diversification of gas supply in South East Europe,;
 Providing access to future Croatian and Albanian gas storage capacities,;
 Economic development in the West Balkan region,;
 Trading hub role for Albania.;

